_sText:
Welcome!

This map is called deathrun_decimate

The objective of this map is for the counter-terrorists to make it to the end of the map and kill the terrorists. But first they will have to endure many traps controlled by the terrorists in the center. There are 32 spawn points for the counter-terrorists and there are two spawn points for the terrorists.

All traps are original with a little help from some people.

Thankyou to:

Astonished
Major Pain
Waffles
Mr. Tissue

for helping me with my map and finding all the glitches to fix.

There is a secret credit room in the map.
But, it will kill you at the same time as the Spawn Room will so get out of there before that happens.
The afks will be killed in 65 seconds.

Thankyou,
Trexx
